# Web-runtime fetch pins -- the immutable upstream sources the vendor build fetches
# browser runtimes from. Sourced by the C/C++/Rust/x86 vendor steps in ALL THREE
# pipelines (ci.yml, pages.yml, export-vendor-bundle.yml) so each pin lives in
# exactly one hashed place: this file is under tools/**, which is in the vendor
# cache key, so changing a pin busts the cache. Never inline one of these in a
# workflow -- see Invariant 10 in docs/architecture.md.
